    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You have got to see this absolute gem. It is in such incredible shape, it honestly looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I have taken meticulous care of it, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you are looking for a ride that is basically brand new without the hefty dealership price tag, this is the one for you. Come take it for a spin\u2014I promise you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 44900.0,
