    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of BMW M-Division engineering, featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and double VANOS variable valve timing. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory limited-slip differential, both operating with flawless mechanical synchronicity. This chassis has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including subframe reinforcement and VANOS solenoid overhaul, ensuring structural rigidity and peak performance. With a pristine interior and a linear power delivery that pulls hard to its 8,000 RPM redline, this vehicle represents a turnkey opportunity for the discerning collector seeking a mechanically perfect driving machine.",
